  "description": "ONSET kick and snare transients pump the OBRIX coral reef filter on every hit. The drums dictate the spectral character of the modular brick synthesis \u2014 the reef brightens with the kick, darkens between beats. No sidechain compressor. The filter follows the drum's amplitude envelope directly, creating a biological push-pull between percussion and synthesis.",
